                                <span>No</span>
                            </label>
                        </p>
                        <span class="helper-text" id="has-spouse-error" style="color: #F44336; font-size: 12px;">Must have a spouse or partner</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="col s12 m6">
                        <p>Is one adult a stay-at-home parent?</p>
                        <p>
